-- ============================================================
-- SECTION 1: WHAT IS THE GOVERNANCE SCHEMA?
-- ============================================================
--
-- The ecomsphere.governance schema is the control layer of the
-- lakehouse.
--
-- It does NOT store business transactions like:
--   - customers
--   - products
--   - orders
--   - payments
--
-- Instead, it stores governance-related control information such as:
--   - dataset metadata
--   - dataset lineage
--   - schema version history
--   - pipeline execution audit
--   - tag registry
--   - governance certification / release readiness
--
-- In simple words:
--
--   Bronze / Silver / Gold tell us:
--     "what the data is"
--
--   Governance tells us:
--     "how the data is controlled, trusted, documented, approved,
--      and monitored"
--
-- ============================================================



