--   - future automation reading Catalog metadata and enriching it
--
-- RECOMMENDED PROJECT APPROACH
-- ------------------------------------------------------------
-- Start with manual SQL inserts for learning and control.
-- Later automate through a metadata registration notebook.
--
-- SIMPLE UNDERSTANDING
